@startuml AI助手服务时序图

title AI助手服务时序图 (AI Assistant Service Sequence Diagram)

' 设置样式
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor LightBlue
}
skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor LightYellow
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor LightGreen
}

actor "用户" as User
participant "前端界面" as Frontend
participant "Flask App" as FlaskApp
participant "QA Engine" as QAEngine
participant "Neo4j Driver" as Neo4jDriver
participant "AI Connector" as AIConnector
participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAIAPI
database "Neo4j Database" as Neo4jDB
participant "Nacos" as Nacos

== 服务启动与注册 ==

FlaskApp -> Nacos: register_to_nacos()
activate FlaskApp
activate Nacos
Nacos --> FlaskApp: 注册成功
FlaskApp -> Nacos: send_heartbeat() (每5秒)
Nacos --> FlaskApp: 心跳确认
deactivate Nacos
deactivate FlaskApp

== 非流式对话流程 (/talk) ==

User -> Frontend: 输入健身问题
Frontend -> FlaskApp: POST /talk\n(问题文本)
activate FlaskApp

FlaskApp -> QAEngine: answer_question(question)
activate QAEngine

QAEngine -> QAEngine: parse_question(question)
QAEngine -> QAEngine: 解析意图、肌群、器械、难度

alt 查询具体动作信息
    QAEngine -> Neo4jDriver: query(Cypher查询)
    activate Neo4jDriver
    Neo4jDriver -> Neo4jDB: MATCH (e:Exercise)
    activate Neo4jDB
    Neo4jDB --> Neo4jDriver: 返回动作详情
    deactivate Neo4jDB
    Neo4jDriver --> QAEngine: 返回查询结果
    deactivate Neo4jDriver
    
    QAEngine -> QAEngine: 格式化答案
    QAEngine --> FlaskApp: neo4j_answer
else 列出符合条件的动作
    QAEngine -> QAEngine: 构建WHERE条件
    QAEngine -> Neo4jDriver: query(Cypher查询)
    activate Neo4jDriver
    Neo4jDriver -> Neo4jDB: MATCH + WHERE查询
    activate Neo4jDB
    Neo4jDB --> Neo4jDriver: 返回动作列表
    deactivate Neo4jDB
    Neo4jDriver --> QAEngine: 返回查询结果
    deactivate Neo4jDriver
    
    QAEngine -> QAEngine: 生成推荐列表
    QAEngine --> FlaskApp: neo4j_answer
end

deactivate QAEngine

FlaskApp -> FlaskApp: build_enhanced_prompt()\n(整合知识库答案)

FlaskApp -> AIConnector: talk(enhanced_question)
activate AIConnector

AIConnector -> OpenAIAPI: chat.completions.create()\n(stream=True, enable_thinking=True)
activate OpenAIAPI

loop 流式接收响应
    OpenAIAPI --> AIConnector: chunk (reasoning_content)
    AIConnector -> AIConnector: 收集思考过程
    OpenAIAPI --> AIConnector: chunk (content)
    AIConnector -> AIConnector: 收集回答内容
end

OpenAIAPI --> AIConnector: usage_info
deactivate OpenAIAPI

AIConnector --> FlaskApp: {"code": 200, "reasoning": "...", "answer": "...", "usage": {...}}
deactivate AIConnector

FlaskApp --> Frontend: JSON响应
deactivate FlaskApp
Frontend --> User: 显示AI回答

== 流式对话流程 (/talkStream) ==

User -> Frontend: 输入健身问题
Frontend -> FlaskApp: POST /talkStream\n(问题文本)
activate FlaskApp

FlaskApp -> QAEngine: answer_question(question)
activate QAEngine

QAEngine -> QAEngine: parse_question(question)
QAEngine -> Neo4jDriver: query(Cypher查询)
activate Neo4jDriver
Neo4jDriver -> Neo4jDB: 执行图谱查询
activate Neo4jDB
Neo4jDB --> Neo4jDriver: 返回查询结果
deactivate Neo4jDB
Neo4jDriver --> QAEngine: 返回neo4j_answer
deactivate Neo4jDriver
QAEngine --> FlaskApp: neo4j_answer
deactivate QAEngine

FlaskApp -> FlaskApp: build_enhanced_prompt()\n(整合知识库答案)

FlaskApp -> AIConnector: talkStream(enhanced_question)
activate AIConnector

AIConnector -> OpenAIAPI: chat.completions.create()\n(stream=True)
activate OpenAIAPI

loop 持续流式输出
    OpenAIAPI --> AIConnector: chunk (content)
    AIConnector -> Frontend: yield data: {type: 'content', data: '...'}\n(SSE格式)
    Frontend --> User: 实时显示文字
end

OpenAIAPI --> AIConnector: [DONE]
AIConnector -> Frontend: yield data: [DONE]
deactivate OpenAIAPI
deactivate AIConnector

deactivate FlaskApp

== 异常处理流程 ==

alt 任何步骤发生异常
    FlaskApp -> FlaskApp: catch Exception
    FlaskApp --> Frontend: {"code": 500, "data": "AI 有点困了~", "msg": "对话失败"}
    Frontend --> User: 显示错误提示
end

note right of QAEngine
  问题解析包括：
  1. 同义词匹配
  2. 正则模板提取
  3. 意图识别
  4. 否定句处理
end note

note right of AIConnector
  AI调用支持：
  1. 思考模式(enable_thinking)
  2. 流式输出
  3. Token用量统计
end note

note right of Neo4jDriver
  图谱查询支持：
  1. 动作信息查询
  2. 多条件筛选
  3. 否定条件排除
end note

@enduml